3B. The Board shall consist of the following members who shall be
appointed by the Minister:
(a) a Chairman;
12                                     Laws of Malaysia                          ACT 343
(b) a representative of the Ministry charged with the
responsibility for the cocoa industry, to be nominated by
the Secretary General of the Ministry;
(c) a representative of the Treasury, to be nominated by the
Secretary General of the Ministry of Finance;
(d) a representative of the Ministry charged with the
responsibility for agriculture, to be nominated by the
Secretary General of the Ministry;
(e) a representative of the Ministry charged with the
responsibility for international trade and industry, to be
nominated by the Secretary General of the Ministry;
(f) five representatives of the cocoa industry;
(g) not more than six persons to represent the other interests
of the cocoa industry or the interests of the Federal
Government or the interests of the State Governments;
and
(h) the Director General.
